to Jerry's sad, smelly crown.

08:28.741 --> 08:31.585
And it's not me.
It's Andy.

08:31.878 --> 08:34.984
Big guy? Check.
Goofy? Check.

08:35.114 --> 08:37.457
All I have to do is wait
for a textbook Dwyer screw-up,

08:37.517 --> 08:40.191
