happens every 20 minutes.

08:40.586 --> 08:42.929
Hey, if it isn't Filo Pilo.

08:42.989 --> 08:45.196
Real creative, Donna.
You expect that to catch on?

08:45.258 --> 08:46.328
Babe, the pen.

08:48.127 --> 08:51.802
Look at Andy. There's ink all over him.
Andy's the new Jerry.

08:51.864 --> 08:53.866
Game over.
Awesome.

08:53.933 --> 08:55.640
Hey, I'm like a giant squid.

08:55.735 --> 08:56.839
Hey, honey,
I'm ink Dracula.

08:56.969 --> 08:58.107
No, stop.

08:58.170 --> 09:00.172
Squid Dracula is going to get you.
(APRIL SCREAMS)

09:00.473 --> 09:01.884
