09:02.108 --> 09:03.416
Barking up
the wrong tree, Filo.

09:03.543 --> 09:04.851
What do you mean?

09:05.144 --> 09:07.750
Andy will never be the new Jerry.
Nothing embarrasses him.

09:07.813 --> 09:09.793
He's like a giant
puppy with no shame.

09:09.849 --> 09:12.591
What you need is some
fresh meat in the office.

09:12.652 --> 09:14.495
Or you guys could just stop
making fun of me.

09:14.554 --> 09:16.090
Yeah. No.

09:17.957 --> 09:21.803
Okay, on to the next Jerry
goal, meet Mayor Knudson.

09:21.928 --> 09:24.909
Oh, yeah. He was the
mayor at the time.

09:24.997 --> 09:26.999
I've always
wanted to meet him.

09:27.133 --> 09:29.340
Well, today you're
getting that chance.

09:30.636 --> 09:33.116
So was he like
a really great mayor?

09:33.272 --> 09:34.478
No, not really.

09:34.540 --> 09:36.611
He resigned because of
corruption and racketeering,

09:36.676 --> 09:38.678
and then he died from
an overdose of pills.

09:38.744 --> 09:40.246
But actually his
real cause of death

09:40.313 --> 09:42.589
was being thrown out of a
helicopter while handcuffed.

09:42.648 --> 09:43.956
<i>Some people say
he's still alive</i>

09:44.083 --> 09:45.426
