never found the body,</i>

09:45.985 --> 09:48.829
but they never found the body
because he exploded on impact.

09:48.888 --> 09:50.526
Sounds like a good dude.
JERRY: Yeah.

09:50.823 --> 09:52.769
I just wish I had
a chance to meet him,

09:52.825 --> 09:56.568
you know, years ago before all
the scandals and his death.

09:57.163 --> 09:58.437
But this is nice too.

09:58.497 --> 09:59.805
Is it?

09:59.932 --> 10:01.240
Yes, it is.
Mmm-hmm.

10:01.667 --> 10:02.941
Okay, go over there.

10:03.002 --> 10:05.608
Let's meet Mayor Knudson.
I'll take your picture.

10:05.671 --> 10:06.706
Butterflies.

10:06.772 --> 10:07.773
(LESLIE AND JERRY LAUGH)

10:07.873 --> 10:09.375
Hello, Mr. Mayor.

10:09.842 --> 10:10.980
