11:16.475 --> 11:21.515
I would have never imagined the
baby-making process to be this clinical.

11:21.580 --> 11:23.753
I mean, imagine if
actual sex were like this.

11:23.816 --> 11:25.261
Let me remove my clothes

11:25.317 --> 11:29.094
