at those physical activities.

11:42.401 --> 11:44.108
(LAUGHS) Yes, we were.

11:45.271 --> 11:46.875
Yes, we were.

11:52.344 --> 11:54.585
You know,
is this all the pamphlets?

11:54.647 --> 11:59.426
